725319f-a.title: Queens: 40th Avenue - 21st Street
725319f-a.text:
40th Avenue, west from 21st Street. 9n the left are
the newly-erected Queensbridge Pouses, a low-rent govern-
mental project.
P. L. Sperr  September 3, 1940
NO REPRODUCTIONS

725120f-a.title: Queens: 21st Street - 40th Avenue
725120f-a.text:
21st Street, west side, north from and across 40th Avenue.
The buildings on the left are on the horth side of 40th Avenue
and on the right is the paper factory of the Ravenswood Paper
Company.
P. L. Sperr  September 5, 1940
NO REPRODUCTIONS
